# Online Mail Promotion System — Cursor Rules

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Vue 3 + Element Plus + Axios (SPA admin dashboard)
- Backend: Node.js + Express
- Database: MySQL 8.0
- Email: SMTP for sending, IMAP for reply polling (planned)
- Real-time: WebSocket + Browser Notification API (planned)

## Architecture Rules
- B/S architecture: Vue SPA frontend, Node.js REST API backend, MySQL database
- Keep backend flat: `src/index.js` + `src/routes/*.js` + `src/db.js` + `src/auth.js`
- AI API keys and email credentials stored server-side only, never exposed to frontend
- File uploads parsed by backend directly

## Frontend Rules
- Use Element Plus components for all UI; maintain consistent Chinese-language admin interface
- Excel upload must show validation progress
- Message center with read/unread filter

## Backend Rules
- Use mysql2 with parameterized queries (no string concatenation for user input)
- Return errors as `{ detail: "..." }` for frontend compatibility
- JWT auth via Bearer token

## Security Rules
- Token-based authentication with admin flag
- Upload file type whitelist — block executables and scripts
- Never log API keys, passwords, or customer emails in plaintext
